# UI file standards

## Tokens

- Link or import `styles.css` (or `@import tokens/*.css`)
- Use `--teal`, `--ink`, `--grad-brand`, `--font-display`, `--section-pad-x`, etc.
- Shadows: accent-tinted (`--shadow-btn`, `--shadow-card`) — never neutral gray

## Typography

- Headings: Stölzl / `--font-display`, weight 300 for large display
- Body: Onest / `--font-body`
- Eyebrows, labels, data: JetBrains Mono, uppercase, `--tracking-label`

## Interaction

- `cursor: pointer` on clickable cards and controls
- Transitions 150–300ms, easing `--ease-out`
- `:focus-visible` outline on interactive elements
- `prefers-reduced-motion` must disable decorative animation

## Components

Prefer existing primitives in `components/` before inventing new patterns.
Match `guidelines/*.html` specimen cards for spacing and radii.
